不要碰我
Get your hand away!

644
00:57:26,385 --> 00:57:29,411
小鬼頭在破壞秩序
The Runts are screwing up
our security, man.

645
00:57:29,622 --> 00:57:30,953
快幫他餵奶
Give the baby his bottle.

646
00:57:31,157 --> 00:57:33,724
叫那些孩子住手
Carrot, just ask the kids
to cool it, okay?

647
00:57:33,759 --> 00:57:37,160
紅毛沒用，任憑小鬼頭搶劫
Carrot’s useless. He lets the Runts
do hold-ups in his section.

648
00:57:37,363 --> 00:57:40,298
員警來會影響生意
The police come around and
that’s bad for business.

649
00:57:40,566 --> 00:57:44,176
我就看
你的面子
I’ll do it only because
I like you.

650
00:57:44,211 --> 00:57:47,786
你快去幫寶寶換尿布
But you need to change
that baby's diapers.

651
00:57:46,372 --> 00:57:50,374
I’ll show you who’s the baby...
你才是寶寶

652
00:57:50,409 --> 00:57:56,013
叫他們別在這裡搶劫強暴
Tell the kids that in my ghetto
no one robs or rapes!

653
00:57:56,115 --> 00:57:57,582
難怪你是※小§霸王
No wonder you’re "Little" Z’!

654
00:58:00,753 --> 00:58:05,690
小鬼頭是一群無法無天的小孩
The Runts were kids who didn't
respect the laws of the ghetto.

655
00:58:05,891 --> 00:58:09,349
他們搶住家，搶麵包店
They would mug residents,
hold up bakeries...

656
00:58:09,562 --> 00:58:11,757
在紅毛那裡特別囂張
especially in Carrot's section.

657
00:58:14,700 --> 00:58:18,261
你們幹什麼？
What are you doing?

658
00:58:20,039 --> 00:58:21,762
老是來搶我
-You rob me all the time!
-But they didn't know...

659
00:58:21,797 --> 00:58:27,099
他們不知道現在這裡有老大了
that the City had a boss now.

660
00:58:28,948 --> 00:58:30,973
（謝謝惠顧）
THANK YOU FOR CHOOSING US

661
00:58:31,183 --> 00:58:35,017
天主之城對居民來說變安全了
The City had become
much safer for residents.

662
00:58:36,355 --> 00:58:39,222
現在幾乎沒有搶劫
There were hardly
any hold-ups now.

663
00:58:39,458 --> 00:58:40,755
有事就找小霸王
You just had to go see Li’l Z'.

664
00:58:40,960 --> 00:58:44,673
-走吧 -別傷害那些小鬼
-Let’s go.
-Don’t hurt the Runts.

665
00:58:44,708 --> 00:58:47,197
我不會碰他們
I won’t touch them.

666
00:58:50,870 --> 00:58:52,838
-牛排 -小霸王
-Hi, Steak.
-How’s it going, Li’l Z’?

667
00:58:53,038 --> 00:58:55,734
-要不要去走走？ -跟你去？
-Wanna take a walk, Steak?
-With you? Hold on...

668
00:58:58,177 --> 00:59:01,169
媽，我跟朋友出去
Mom, I’m going out with
my friends.

669
00:59:13,626 --> 00:59:16,288
真好吃的雞
That’s the best chicken
I ever ate.

670
00:59:16,762 --> 00:59:21,373
那個老頭嚇死了
你替他難過？
-The old guy was scared shitless.
-Feeling sorry for him?

671
00:59:21,408 --> 00:59:24,059
怎麼可能
You’re crazy, man!

672
00:59:32,478 --> 00:59:35,345
乾脆去搶銀行或超市
Why not stick up
a bank or a supermarket?

673
00:59:35,548 --> 00:59:39,985
-太遜了，毒品才好賺
-沒錯，販毒
-Peanuts. Drugs are where it’s at.
-Yeah, selling drugs.

674
00:59:40,186 --> 00:59:46,489
但得從小弟做起
你要嗎？
But you have to start out as a delivery
boy. You wanna be a delivery boy?

675
00:59:46,692 --> 00:59:51,925
真剝削，熬好久才能爬上去
It’s a rip off.
It takes a long time to move up.

676
00:59:52,231 --> 00:59:56,102
老鳥死了才能往上爬
You have to wait till an older guy
gets killed to move up.

677
00:59:56,137 --> 01:00:02,868
我不想等
我要學小霸王，把他們幹掉
croaks. I'm gonna do what Li’l Z' did.
I don't wanna wait till some guy
I'm gonna wipe them all out.

678
01:00:03,075 --> 01:00:05,908
在講我嗎？老大我來了
Talking about me, kid?
The boss is here.

679
01:00:10,015 --> 01:00:11,573
小鬼，回來
Come back, you brat!

680
01:00:15,955 --> 01:00:21,728
-動作真快
-真會跑
-They’re quick, those kids.
-They run fast.

681
01:00:21,763 --> 01:00:27,501
別的都跑了 還有嗎？
They’re all gone except you.
Any others?

682
01:00:34,340 --> 01:00:37,002
你們得替他們付出代價
You’re gonna pay
for the ones that escaped.

683
01:00:37,209 --> 01:00:41,373
自己選，要射手還是腳？
You choose. Shall I shoot you
in the hand or foot?

684
01:00:41,981 --> 01:00:43,881
快選
Come on, choose!

685
01:00:44,083 --> 01:00:47,331
手還是腳？
Hand or foot?

686
01:00:49,388 --> 01:00:52,118
趕快選，快選啊
Choose, for fuck's sake!

687
01:00:59,865 --> 01:01:02,993
-手 -你選小手？
-Hand.
-The little hand, eh?

688
01:01:10,981 --> 01:01:13,970
酷斃了
Cool.

689
01:01:13,992 --> 01:01:19,650
牛排，來看看你的能耐
Hey, Steak’n’fries,
let’s see what you’re made of.

690
01:01:19,685 --> 01:01:23,185
殺了其中一個
Choose and then kill
one of them.

691
01:01:23,389 --> 01:01:27,476
-滾開，讓他來
-算了，讓我來
-Leave it. I’ll do it.
-Butt out, Tuba. This is for him.

692
01:01:30,029 --> 01:01:31,860
快點
Go on, Steak.

693
01:01:32,064 --> 01:01:35,500
選一個，然後開槍
Go on, choose one and shoot.

694
01:01:35,701 --> 01:01:38,727
快點，我沒時間等你
Come on, I haven’t got all day.

695
01:01:38,937 --> 01:01:43,461
快啊
看你要殺哪一個
Kill one of them.

696
01:01:45,010 --> 01:01:48,104
快，我的時間有限
Let’s go, Steak.
I’m in a hurry.

697
01:01:48,314 --> 01:01:51,681
我想看你有沒有種
I wanna see what you’re made of.

698
01:01:53,762 --> 01:01:56,663
殺了其中一個

699
01:01:56,893 --> 01:01:59,259
快點，我趕時間

700
01:01:59,358 --> 01:02:04,395
很好，你辦到了
Well done!
You did it.

701
01:02:04,430 --> 01:02:12,577
-你也是兄弟了
-很好，牛排
-You’re one of us. Give me five.
-Very good, Steak.

702
01:02:12,805 --> 01:02:19,810
起來，回你的老鼠洞去
不准跛腳
Get up, brat. Go back
to your rat hole. Without limping!

703
01:02:20,312 --> 01:02:24,612
叫其他人不准在我的地方搶劫
Tell your buddies that no one
robs in Li’l Z”s ghetto.

704
01:02:24,817 --> 01:02:27,581
快去，不准跛腳
Go now.
And no limping, okay?

705
01:02:29,888 --> 01:02:32,118
Cool, Li’l Z'.

706
01:02:44,703 --> 01:02:48,366
小霸王贏得居民的尊敬
While Li’l Z' was winning
the respect of the residents...

707
01:02:48,841 --> 01:02:51,810
班尼則贏得安潔莉卡的心
Benny was winning
Angelica's heart.

708
01:02:52,344 --> 01:02:56,974
而我，仍是個窮光蛋處男
As for me, I was still
a virgin, single and broke.

709
01:02:57,182 --> 01:02:59,446
我別無選擇
I had no choice.

710
01:03:00,552 --> 01:03:03,487
（一個俗辣的人生）
SUCKER’S LIFE

711
01:03:03,689 --> 01:03:07,420
我必須去超市上班
I had to take a job
in a supermarket.

712
01:03:07,626 --> 01:03:12,154
工時長，薪水少
我巴不得被解雇
I worked long hours for chicken feed.
I wanted to be laid off...

713
01:03:12,364 --> 01:03:16,391
好用遣散費買一台相機
so I could buy a camera
with the severance pay.

714
01:03:17,603 --> 01:03:20,731
但我想得太美了
But things didn't
work out that way.

715
01:03:23,809 --> 01:03:26,471
-是海邊那個人 -老兄
-It’s the guy on the beach.
-Hey, bro!

716
01:03:26,678 --> 01:03:29,374
-還在抽好貨？ -是啊
-Still smoking good stuff?
-Yeah.

717
01:03:29,581 --> 01:03:31,242
這傢伙太酷了
That guy’s too cool.

718
01:03:31,450 --> 01:03:34,010
小朋友，衣服拉起來
Hey, kid. Come here.
Lift up your shirt.

719
01:03:39,024 --> 01:03:42,391
這些貧民窟小孩，給臉不要臉
We give these ghetto kids a chance
and they don't appreciate it.

720
01:03:42,594 --> 01:03:46,086
-那遣散費呢？ -什麼遣散費？
-What about my severance pay?
-What severance pay?

721
01:03:46,298 --> 01:03:50,257
經理以為我跟他們是一夥的
That fucking manager thought
I was part of the gang.

722
01:03:50,469 --> 01:03:55,634
你因嚴重失職被解雇 馬上給我滾
You’re fired for serious misconduct.
Get out. Immediately!

723
01:03:55,841 --> 01:03:59,299
我一分錢也沒拿到
I didn’t get a single cent.

724
01:04:13,091 --> 01:04:15,252
這仿佛一道神諭
It was like a message from God:

725
01:04:17,563 --> 01:04:21,397
※蠢材，誠實沒有好下場§
"Honesty doesn't pay, sucker’."

726
01:04:21,600 --> 01:04:24,865
（意圖犯罪）
FLIRTING WITH CRIME

727
01:04:34,046 --> 01:04:38,352
我等了好久
上班都遲到了
The bus sure took a long time to come.
I should already be at work.

728
01:04:38,584 --> 01:04:41,985
把槍藏好，你瘋啦？
Shit, hide that gun.
Are you nuts?

729
01:04:42,187 --> 01:04:43,848
這是阿呆的，反正壞了
It was Goose’s.
It’s broken anyway.

730
01:04:44,056 --> 01:04:47,324
是這個路線的班次少
It’s not our fault, the company
runs few buses on this line.

731
01:04:47,359 --> 01:04:51,955
誰都沒有錯，都是別人的錯
It’s never anyone’s fault.
It’s always someone else’s.

732
01:04:52,164 --> 01:04:56,123
苦的是勞工，還要被壓榨
But it’s the workers who suffer.
And then, they make us squeeze!

733
01:04:56,335 --> 01:04:58,462
祝您晚安
Have a nice evening, ma'am.

734
01:05:00,973 --> 01:05:03,339
我認識他，他也住天主之城
I know that guy.

735
01:05:03,542 --> 01:05:05,809
會認出我們
He lives in the City.
He’ll recognize us.

736
01:05:05,844 --> 01:05:08,438
他才不會在乎老闆的錢被搶
So? He couldn’t care less
if we take his boss’ money.

737
01:05:08,647 --> 01:05:11,161
好，走吧
Okay. Let’s go.

738
01:05:13,819 --> 01:05:17,277
你們不是住天主之城？
Well, boys? Aren’t you from
the City of God?

739
01:05:17,723 --> 01:05:19,020
是啊
Yeah.

740
01:05:19,224 --> 01:05:22,387
我讓你們一個人免費
I’ll let one of you through
without paying.

741
01:05:26,665 --> 01:05:30,795
你們要念書，才能離開貧民區
You should study
so you can get out of the ghetto.

742
01:05:31,003 --> 01:05:33,870
那裡條子和流氓太多了
It's too full of cops and
hoodlums.

743
01:05:34,072 --> 01:05:37,940
你念過書嗎？
我上過學，當過兵
-Did you study?
-I was in school and in the army.

744
01:05:38,143 --> 01:05:41,306
是營上的第一神射
I was the best marksman
in my barracks.

745
01:05:41,513 --> 01:05:44,038
我只找得到這份工作
This job was all
I could find afterwards.

746
01:05:44,249 --> 01:05:48,447
但我在練空手道，有別的工作
But I do karate.
If I’m hired somewhere...

747
01:05:48,654 --> 01:05:50,747
我就離開貧民窟
I’ll leave the ghetto.

748
01:05:51,256 --> 01:05:55,787
-我愛好愛與和平
-你打不打架？
-Do you fight, then?
-I’m for peace and love.

749
01:05:56,094 --> 01:05:57,561
但必要時…
But if I have to...

750
01:05:57,763 --> 01:06:00,017
會有那麼一天的
He didn't know he would have to.

751
01:06:00,052 --> 01:06:04,352
不過還沒輪到帥奈德的故事
But not yet, it's not time
to tell Knockout Ned's story.

752
01:06:04,903 --> 01:06:07,064
-我們該走了 -走吧
-We should be going.
-Let’s go.

753
01:06:07,272 --> 01:06:08,972
-再見 -謝了
-Good bye.
-Thanks.

754
01:06:09,007 --> 01:06:09,971
拜拜
See you.

755
01:06:15,247 --> 01:06:17,977
我下不了手，他人很好
I couldn’t do it.
He was such a cool guy.

756
01:06:18,183 --> 01:06:21,346
是啊，他是葛森的哥哥
Yeah, totally.
That’s Gerson’s brother.

757
01:06:22,220 --> 01:06:24,552
回家吧
Let’s go home.

758
01:06:26,692 --> 01:06:30,753
這裡只有那家麵包店
There’s nothing here
except that bakery over there.

759
01:06:30,963 --> 01:06:35,832
-不知道，※搶劫§吧
-要說什麼？
-What will you say?
-I don’t know. "This is a hold-up."

760
01:06:37,936 --> 01:06:39,528
這是我的電話
Here’s my number.

761
01:06:39,738 --> 01:06:41,933
-你喜歡靈魂還是爵士派對？ -靈魂派對
-You like soul or groovy parties?
-Soul.

762
01:06:42,307 --> 01:06:44,070
這個也沒成功
That one didn't work either.

763
01:06:44,276 --> 01:06:47,609
女店員好妖嬌，還跟我調情
The counter girl was just too foxy.
And she flirted with me.

764
01:06:47,813 --> 01:06:48,973
你會打給我嗎？
Will you call me?

765
01:06:50,215 --> 01:06:54,249
我沒辦法對她掏槍，她好甜
I couldn’t pull a gun on her,
she was too sweet.

766
01:06:54,284 --> 01:06:56,093
我同意
Yeah, I agree.

767
01:06:58,363 --> 01:07:05,763
請問一下
我迷路了，巴哈怎麼走？
Excuse me. I’m lost.
How do I get to Barra?

768
01:07:05,964 --> 01:07:06,953
-巴哈？ -是啊
-To Barra?
-Yes.

769
01:07:07,165 --> 01:07:09,963
我心想，算這個聖保羅人衰
I thought: "Tough luck
for this guy from Sao Paulo."

770
01:07:10,168 --> 01:07:13,337
-這麼巧
-我們正要過去
-In fact, we were going there.
-You’re kidding.

771
01:07:14,840 --> 01:07:17,775
-你救了我一命 -沒錯
-You’re a lifesaver.
-That’s right.

772
01:07:18,543 --> 01:07:21,944
因為聖保羅人都很爛
Because no guy from Sao Paulo
could ever be cool.

773
01:07:29,421 --> 01:07:31,867
屍體在這邊
-The body’s over here.
-We found it, Chief.

774
01:07:31,902 --> 01:07:35,349
警長，找到了
法醫先生
The forensic expert!

775
01:07:50,842 --> 01:07:52,935
長得不怎麼樣嘛
-Not a pretty sight, eh?
-You said it.

776
01:07:53,145 --> 01:07:55,612
-好棒的歌手 -你喜歡他？
-What a great singer.
-You like him?

777
01:07:55,647 --> 01:08:01,170
我喜歡音樂，你呢？
你也喜歡大麻嗎？
-I love music. What about you?
-Tell me, do you also like pot?

778
01:08:04,289 --> 01:08:06,780
我不能說沒抽過
I can’t say I’ve never tried it.

779
01:08:06,992 --> 01:08:10,120
你自己找吧
The devil recognizes his own.

780
01:08:12,197 --> 01:08:14,965
有紙嗎？
-Do you have papers?
-I think so.

781
01:08:15,000 --> 01:08:18,551
我用完了
我這裡有
I have some.

782
01:08:20,038 --> 01:08:22,802
我很會卷大麻
I’d always been an ace
at rolling a joint.

783
01:08:23,008 --> 01:08:25,408
要是泡妞也這麼行
If I’d had the same skill
with girls...

784
01:08:26,211 --> 01:08:30,375
就不會錯失這麼多上床機會了
I’d never have lost so many chances
to lose my virginity.

785
01:08:32,484 --> 01:08:37,251
-以聖保羅人來說你很酷
-謝了
-For a Sao Paulo guy you’re very cool.
-Thanks, bro.

786
01:08:37,456 --> 01:08:40,414
兇器是什麼？
What did they use?

787
01:08:40,726 --> 01:08:44,312
木棒或石頭
孩子呢？
A club or a rock.
And the child?

788
01:08:44,347 --> 01:08:47,898
-毫髮無傷 -謝天謝地
-Untouched.
-Thank goodness.

789
01:08:48,366 --> 01:08:52,216
死了多久？
大約4小時
-How long ago?
-About four hours.

790
01:08:52,251 --> 01:08:56,067
-可以搬走了嗎？ -搬吧
-Can we take it away?
-Go ahead.

791
01:08:57,442 --> 01:09:01,675
兇手一定是天主之城的人
The murderer has to be
from the City of God.

792
01:09:20,165 --> 01:09:24,693
混蛋，媽的
You bastard!
You motherfucker!

793
01:09:25,403 --> 01:09:28,787
你一定要在這裡殺人嗎？
Did you have to kill
your chick in the ghetto?

794
01:09:28,822 --> 01:09:31,532
引來一大堆條子
-The place is crawling with cops now!
-Come on, Li’l Z'.

795
01:09:31,743 --> 01:09:36,203
別這樣
去你的
我得維護名譽
-Come on? Fuck you!
-I had to avenge my honor.

796
01:09:36,414 --> 01:09:39,906
她家人去告我了，你很安全
Her family’s turned me in.
You won’t have any problems.

797
01:09:40,118 --> 01:09:43,610
你把員警引來，你死定了
The cops are everywhere because
of you. You’re dead meat, asshole.

798
01:09:43,822 --> 01:09:46,689
算了，你也打夠了
Let up, Li’l Z’.
You’ve punished him enough.

799
01:09:46,892 --> 01:09:49,197
你知道規矩
You know the law.

800
01:09:49,227 --> 01:09:51,889
在我的地方殺人就得死
Anyone who kills in my ghetto
has to die as an example.

801
01:09:52,097 --> 01:09:54,795
那是他的事
That was his business, Li’l Z’.

802
01:09:54,900 --> 01:09:57,494
聽著，離開貧民區
Listen, you sonofabitch,
