-孩子？我哈草嗑藥，殺人放火
-Are you crazy? You’re just a kid.
-A kid? I smoke, snort...

968
01:29:46,584 --> 01:29:50,054
我是男人
I’ve killed and robbed.
I’m a man.

969
01:29:50,259 --> 01:29:52,784
你懂個屁
Shit, you have no idea!

970
01:29:52,995 --> 01:29:57,148
他很忠心，你應該加入我們
He’s attached to his gang.
You should join up with us.

971
01:29:56,432 --> 01:30:01,301
要殺他嗎？
你要變絞肉了
-Shall we kill him?
-Steak, we're going to grind you.

972
01:30:01,808 --> 01:30:07,137
好，我接受
太好了
-Okay, I accept.
-Great!

973
01:30:07,343 --> 01:30:12,595
回去說該帥奈德和紅毛當家了
Tell your boss that Knockout Ned
and Carrot are now in command.

974
01:30:11,647 --> 01:30:17,847
有一個條件，不准濫殺無辜
But on one condition:
no killing of innocent people.

975
01:30:18,404 --> 01:30:22,082
我無法接受亂殺人
I can't accept that, understand?

976
01:30:22,117 --> 01:30:26,955
不殺無辜
Okay, no innocent people.

977
01:30:28,364 --> 01:30:33,301
牛排搞砸了
Steak fucked up!

978
01:30:43,976 --> 01:30:47,574
有我的槍嗎？
-Have you a gun for me?
-No...

979
01:30:45,716 --> 01:30:51,184
沒有，不過可以去搶
but we can hold up
a gun store.

980
01:30:51,219 --> 01:30:52,847
小事一樁
That’s no problem.

981
01:30:52,882 --> 01:30:57,251
我不想搶劫 我不是兄弟
I don’t want to hold up anything.
I’m not a hoodlum.

982
01:30:57,286 --> 01:31:00,656
這是我和他的私事
This is a personal affair
between me and him, okay?

983
01:31:00,691 --> 01:31:03,594
我不是兄弟
I’m not a hoodlum.

984
01:31:04,782 --> 01:31:07,936
他奸了你的妞
He raped your chick...

985
01:31:07,043 --> 01:31:11,971
殺了你的叔叔弟弟，轟爛你家
killed your uncle and brother,
gunned your house...

986
01:31:12,006 --> 01:31:15,541
而你只殺了他一個手下
and you killed one of his guys.

987
01:31:18,872 --> 01:31:23,510
你不是兄弟就出去
If you’re not a hood,
then get out.

988
01:31:27,396 --> 01:31:33,027
（帥奈德的故事）
THE STORY OF KNOCKOUT NED

989
01:31:34,195 --> 01:31:36,686
搶劫
This is a hold-up!

990
01:31:43,853 --> 01:31:48,368
第一次…
左輪呢？
-The first time...
-Where are the revolvers?

991
01:31:48,576 --> 01:31:52,205
帥奈德救了一個店員
...Knockout Ned saved a salesclerk
from being shot by Carrot.

992
01:31:52,413 --> 01:31:55,614
說好不殺人的
We said no killing!

993
01:31:55,649 --> 01:31:58,815
這是規則
That’s the rule.

994
01:31:59,195 --> 01:32:08,394
我們來搶老闆的錢
你們希望我們走？我們也是
We want the boss’ money. Everyone
keep calm. Open the cash register!
You want us to go?
We do too.

995
01:32:08,596 --> 01:32:11,030
所以動作快
So hurry up!

996
01:32:11,408 --> 01:32:16,803
看地上
第二次，紅毛救了帥奈德
-Look at the ground!
-The second time...
Carrot saved
Knockout Ned's life.

997
01:32:18,784 --> 01:32:22,702
奈德學到每個規則都有例外
Ned learned that there's
an exception to every rule.

998
01:32:22,737 --> 01:32:25,676
這是例外
Exception to the rule.

999
01:32:25,880 --> 01:32:28,317
-你是經理？ -對
-Are you the manager?
-Yes.

1000
01:32:28,352 --> 01:32:33,176
這是搶劫
統統趴在地上
This is a hold-up.
Everyone on the ground!

1001
01:32:33,211 --> 01:32:35,413
趴下
On the ground!

1002
01:32:35,623 --> 01:32:39,855
把錢給我
Give me the money!

1003
01:32:42,797 --> 01:32:45,027
我不是在說笑，誰動就讓他死
I’m not kidding.

1004
01:32:45,233 --> 01:32:51,498
第三次，例外成了規則
The first person who moves
is dead!
The third time, the exception
becomes the rule.

1005
01:33:06,274 --> 01:33:11,657
利用搶來的錢 他們準備跟小霸王拼了
prepared to face Li’l Z'.
Carrot and Knockout Ned

1006
01:33:11,859 --> 01:33:14,068
紅毛可以保住生意
Carrot could protect his
business.

1007
01:33:14,103 --> 01:33:19,833
營上第一神射的帥奈德 則想報仇
Knockout Ned...
the best marksman in his battalion,
wanted revenge.

1008
01:33:20,034 --> 01:33:23,618
先是義大利槍，9釐米的
First, the Italians.
This is a 9 mm.

1009
01:33:23,653 --> 01:33:27,203
-我看看 -不錯吧？
-Let me see.
-Not bad, eh?

1010
01:33:26,523 --> 01:33:32,107
-準星有問題
-我算你特價
-The sight isn’t well-aligned.
-I’ll give you a good price.

1011
01:33:32,333 --> 01:33:36,778
12釐米※打炮槍§…懂了吧？
The 12 mm, the "hand job".
See why?

1012
01:33:36,224 --> 01:33:40,045
9釐米烏茲衝鋒槍，以色列貨
An Uzi, 9 mm. It’s Israeli.

1013
01:33:40,080 --> 01:33:42,384
大衛之星
猶太貨
-The star of David.
-Jewish.

1014
01:33:42,419 --> 01:33:44,972
我要30-06步槍
I want a 30-06.

1015
01:33:45,007 --> 01:33:47,525
可以大幹一場了
Now we can start having fun.

1016
01:33:47,729 --> 01:33:51,503
要開戰了，先來禱告
The war’s on.
Let’s start with a prayer.

1017
01:33:51,538 --> 01:33:57,926
我們在天上的父
願人都遵你的名為聖
Our Father who art in heaven
hallowed be our name...

1018
01:33:56,738 --> 01:34:00,902
願我們的旨意行在地上
Our will be done...

1019
01:34:00,937 --> 01:34:05,179
如同行在天上
On earth as it is in heaven...

1020
01:34:16,519 --> 01:34:19,250
流氓有槍，但不會用
Hoodlums have guns,
but can't shoot.

1021
01:34:18,780 --> 01:34:23,587
帥奈德開一槍能抵小霸王十槍
was worth ten from Li’l Z”s gang.
One bullet from Knockout Ned

1022
01:34:23,389 --> 01:34:27,928
小霸王氣不過，展開反擊
Li’l Z' couldn't take it.
He counter-attacked.

1023
01:34:29,774 --> 01:34:34,803
貧民區從人間煉獄落入地獄
The ghetto had been a purgatory,
now it was hell.

1024
01:34:37,950 --> 01:34:44,446
我決心離開，所以去當記者
I decided to get out.
That's how I became a reporter.

1025
01:34:44,526 --> 01:34:50,423
好棒的照片，一定是羅葛瑞的
I bet it’s by Rogerio Reis.
Great photo!

1026
01:34:50,458 --> 01:34:53,825
我就說吧
What did I tell you?

1027
01:34:53,155 --> 01:34:59,867
我跟其他行家一樣從基層做起
Like any pro...
I started at the bottom,
way down at the bottom.

1028
01:34:58,924 --> 01:35:03,526
未來仍是一片茫然
Without knowing what awaited me.

1029
01:35:04,288 --> 01:35:08,142
我不回家，跑去報社
I’d go over to the paper.
Instead of going home

1030
01:35:07,697 --> 01:35:11,709
研究室有個來自天主之城的人
A guy from the City of God
worked in the lab.

1031
01:35:11,744 --> 01:35:13,925
你看
Check this out.

1032
01:35:13,960 --> 01:35:19,043
他讓我更接近生命中的最愛
He helped me move closer to
what I loved most in life.

1033
01:35:19,078 --> 01:35:20,880
-羅葛瑞 -你好嗎？
-Hi, Rogerio.
-How are you, Pierre?

1034
01:35:21,089 --> 01:35:23,717
這是阿炮，他是攝影師
This is Rocket.
He’s a photographer.

1035
01:35:23,752 --> 01:35:24,711
阿炮，你好
Hello, Rocket.

1036
01:35:24,746 --> 01:35:27,557
-他很喜歡你 -真的？
-He’s a fan of yours.
-Really?

1037
01:35:27,592 --> 01:35:29,024
你真有品味
You have good taste, Rocket!

1038
01:35:29,059 --> 01:35:32,691
-我先走了 -再見
-Well, I’m done. I’m off.
-See you.

1039
01:35:32,726 --> 01:35:35,562
他人真好
What a cool guy!

1040
01:35:35,566 --> 01:35:42,165
單純的復仇演變成大火拼
What should have been
a swift revenge...
turned into an all-out war.

1041
01:35:46,595 --> 01:35:50,056
天主之城一分為二
The City of God was divided.

1042
01:35:50,091 --> 01:35:53,021
兩區不能相通
You couldn't go from one
section to the other.

1043
01:35:53,056 --> 01:35:55,951
連拜訪親戚都不行
Not even to visit a relative.

1044
01:35:55,257 --> 01:35:59,888
員警把貧民區的人都當流氓
The cops considered anyone
living in the ghetto a hoodlum.

1045
01:35:59,923 --> 01:36:03,530
大家過著越戰的生活
People got used to living
in Vietnam.

1046
01:36:06,947 --> 01:36:12,695
越來越多人自願送死
And more and more volunteers
kept signing up to die.

1047
01:36:10,456 --> 01:36:13,896
他要找你
有什麼事？
This kid...

1048
01:36:14,108 --> 01:36:16,425
我被紅毛的小弟揍
-What do you want?
-A boy from Carrot’s gang punched me.

1049
01:36:16,460 --> 01:36:18,743
火拼成了藉口
The war was
an excuse for everything.

1050
01:36:19,147 --> 01:36:21,115
小霸王的打手踹我
One of Li’l Z”s soldiers
kicked me.

1051
01:36:22,499 --> 01:36:25,176
拿這把點22
Take this .22.

1052
01:36:26,257 --> 01:36:29,456
紅毛的人強暴我姊
The jerk who raped my sister is
with Carrot.

1053
01:36:29,657 --> 01:36:30,814
小霸王趕走我家
Li’l Z’ evicted my family.

1054
01:36:30,849 --> 01:36:33,720
我想殺人，讓別人怕我
Kill... Be respected.

1055
01:36:46,107 --> 01:36:51,568
我是提亞哥，班尼的朋友
-你認識字嗎？會加減嗎？
-I’m Thiago, a friend of Benny’s.
-Can you read? Can you add?

1056
01:36:51,779 --> 01:36:56,874
-我蠻會管生意的
-那就開工吧
-I’m pretty good in business.
-Okay, get to work.

1057
01:36:56,909 --> 01:37:04,253
-幹掉殺父仇人-你想幹嘛？
-你叫什麼？-奧圖
-To get my father’s murderer.
-What’s your name?
-My name’s Otto.
-What do you want?

1058
01:37:08,981 --> 01:37:11,665
怎麼回事？
What’s the matter?

1059
01:37:10,895 --> 01:37:15,825
-他是個工人 -他想要槍
-He’s a worker.
-But he wants a gun.

1060
01:37:15,860 --> 01:37:19,233
他撐不了1星期
He won’t last a week.

1061
01:37:29,474 --> 01:37:35,086
1年後，沒有人記得前因後果
A year later, no one
remembered how it had all begun.

1062
01:37:35,289 --> 01:37:36,620
去死吧
Take that!

1063
01:37:38,589 --> 01:37:45,366
兩邊都想搶對方的生意
For both sides, the aim was to take
over the enemy's business in order...

1064
01:37:43,876 --> 01:37:49,093
好買更多槍，搶更多生意
to buy more guns and take over
more businesses.

1065
01:38:10,041 --> 01:38:14,375
我哈草嗑藥，殺人放火
I’ve killed and robbed.
I smoke, snort,

1066
01:38:14,410 --> 01:38:16,660
我是男人
I’m a man.

1067
01:38:37,492 --> 01:38:43,347
媒體開始報導，警方只好干涉
The media started taking an interest.
The police had to intervene.

1068
01:38:57,305 --> 01:39:00,471
一名天主之城的角頭被捕
A gang leader, from the City of God,
was arrested today.

1069
01:39:00,506 --> 01:39:03,638
人稱帥奈德的曼紐馬恰多
Manuel Machado,
a.k.a. Knockout Ned...

1070
01:39:03,844 --> 01:39:06,761
遭小霸王的人槍傷送醫
was hospitalized after being
wounded by Li’l Z”s gang.

1071
01:39:06,796 --> 01:39:09,678
本台記者專訪到他
Our reporter interviewed him.

1072
01:39:09,325 --> 01:39:13,843
火拼還在持續嗎？
還在持續
-Is the war still going on?
-It's still going on.

1073
01:39:13,292 --> 01:39:21,184
死了多少人？
很多，大多是無辜者
-Have many people died?
-Many have died.
Mostly innocent people.

1074
01:39:21,195 --> 01:39:24,562
光是認識我就會被小霸王殺
Just knowing me is enough...

1075
01:39:24,765 --> 01:39:29,498
to get you killed by Li’l Z'.

1076
01:39:29,704 --> 01:39:34,722
-警方都不管嗎？
-他們捉我，不捉他
-The police don’t go in there?
-They go after me, not him.

1077
01:39:33,274 --> 01:39:39,611
I’ve been in jail, while he goes
我坐牢，他拼命殺人
on killing undisturbed.

1078
01:39:39,814 --> 01:39:41,438
員警卻不捉
And they don’t arrest him.

1079
01:39:41,473 --> 01:39:44,414
帥奈德說火拼將持續
Knockout Ned says
the war will continue.

1080
01:39:44,618 --> 01:39:50,215
蓋德警長保證將逮捕雙方人馬
Police Chief Guedes has promised
to arrest both of the gangs.

1081
01:39:58,035 --> 01:40:00,428
媽的
Motherfucker!

1082
01:39:59,914 --> 01:40:04,195
老大是我，上報的卻是他
I’m the boss here, but he gets
his picture in the paper!

1083
01:40:04,405 --> 01:40:07,966
-有我的照片嗎？ -只有帥奈德的
-Have you found mine?
-Just Knockout Ned’s.

1084
01:40:08,175 --> 01:40:12,774
繼續找，至少名字要見報
Keep looking.

1085
01:40:10,044 --> 01:40:12,774
At least my name’s
got to be in there.

1086
01:40:12,980 --> 01:40:14,675
-什麼都沒有 -你認識字嗎？
-There’s nothing.
-Can you read?

1087
01:40:14,882 --> 01:40:17,316
只認得照片
Just the pictures.

1088
01:40:18,285 --> 01:40:20,344
什麼都沒有
Nothing.

1089
01:40:20,554 --> 01:40:23,258
喂，你幹什麼？
Hey, what the fuck are you doing?

1090
01:40:23,293 --> 01:40:28,989
那是分類廣告
我不管，要全都看過
-It’s just the want ads.
-I don’t care, read everything!

1091
01:40:28,361 --> 01:40:33,360
-上面又沒有新聞
-你想挨子彈嗎？
-But there aren’t any articles.
-Want a bullet in your head?

1092
01:40:34,670 --> 01:40:38,861
讓他們知道誰是老大
Gotta show them who’s boss here.

1093
01:40:43,055 --> 01:40:47,608
-把相機給我 -不要
-Give me the camera!
-No way!

1094
01:40:50,151 --> 01:40:52,483
幫我照相
Take my picture, man.

1095
01:40:52,518 --> 01:40:55,817
我按不下去
I can’t work it.

1096
01:40:55,852 --> 01:40:57,718
快點
Go ahead.

1097
01:40:58,092 --> 01:41:02,654
-我來穩住法冠
-我試試看
-I’ll hold the Beretta.
-Let me try...

1098
01:41:02,689 --> 01:41:05,993
讓開
Back off...

1099
01:41:05,530 --> 01:41:10,466
-按不下去
-真是一群飯桶
-There’s no click.
-What a bunch of bozos!

1100
01:41:10,501 --> 01:41:13,735
帶著你們穩死的
I’m fucked with you guys.

1101
01:41:15,810 --> 01:41:18,370
我知道了
I have an idea.

1102
01:41:18,579 --> 01:41:23,107
我去找朋友來，別急
I’ll go get a guy I know.
Hang loose.

1103
01:41:23,170 --> 01:41:27,886
他來了
相機拿去
-Here he is.
-Take the camera.

1104
01:41:27,131 --> 01:41:31,023
小子，如何？
Well, kid?

1105
01:41:31,450 --> 01:41:37,496
你不是攝影師嗎？讓相機動，我們不會弄
Aren’t you a photographer?
Make the camerawork. We can’t do it.

1106
01:41:39,300 --> 01:41:41,097
幫我們照相
Take our picture.

1107
01:41:45,401 --> 01:41:49,840
-你弄壞了 -不是我
-It wasn’t me.
-You fucking broke it.

1108
01:41:49,875 --> 01:41:56,109
要轉一下
I found it.
It has to be wound.

1109
01:42:00,554 --> 01:42:04,207
-你叫什麼？ -阿炮
-What’s your name?
-Rocket.

1110
01:42:04,242 --> 01:42:06,311
阿炮，再來一張
-Another picture, Rocket.
-How about two rows?

1111
01:42:06,346 --> 01:42:12,965
-排成兩排好了 -什麼？
排成兩排，把槍拿著
-What?
-Two rows. Everyone with their guns.

1112
01:42:13,096 --> 01:42:17,761
-喂，你出鏡了
-口氣好一點
-You’re outside, for Christ’s sake!
-Talk to him nicely, kid.

1113
01:42:17,972 --> 01:42:19,906
抱歉，請站進來
Sorry. Move in, please.

1114
01:42:22,409 --> 01:42:24,877
再一張
Another one.

1115
01:42:28,195 --> 01:42:31,548
-底片沒了
-那就拿出來看
-I think the roll’s finished.
-Then show us the pictures.

1116
01:42:31,752 --> 01:42:33,310
得拿去洗
-They have to be developed.
-Developed?

1117
01:42:33,345 --> 01:42:37,517
洗？要多少錢？
How much is it?

1118
01:42:37,415 --> 01:42:43,270
這些錢拿去，洗好拿給我
我拿底片
Take this money.
And bring back the pictures.

1119
01:42:42,730 --> 01:42:47,997
不必，整台拿去
-I have to remove the film.
-Keep the camera.

1120
01:42:47,958 --> 01:42:52,905
班尼不是要送你？拿去吧
didn’t he? So, it’s yours...
Benny wanted to give it to you,

1121
01:42:52,940 --> 01:42:54,938
謝了
Thanks.

1122
01:42:56,877 --> 01:43:01,075
別忘了拿照片來
相片，阿炮
Don’t forget the pictures.
The photos, Rocket!

1123
01:43:11,093 --> 01:43:14,677
-皮耶 -怎樣？
-Pierre!
-What?

1124
01:43:14,712 --> 01:43:18,568
可以幫我洗嗎？
Can you develop this for me?

1125
01:43:18,603 --> 01:43:21,774
不行，會惹上麻煩
I can’t, Rocket.
I could get into trouble.

1126
